Proof:
  f is a map and (the domain of f is equal to \ORDomega) and for all v0, (if v0 is an object then (if v0 is an element of the domain of f then (the value of f under v0 is equal to \ORDsucc( v0 ))))
  X is a subset of \ORDomega and X is inductive regarding \SETempty and f
